'''2016年国际象棋世界冠军赛'''（{{lang-en|World Chess Championship 2016}}）是决定2016年[[国际象棋世界冠军|国际象棋世界冠军]]的比赛，由卫冕冠军[[马格努斯·卡尔森|马格努斯·卡尔森]]对阵挑战者[[谢尔盖·卡尔亚金|谢尔盖·卡尔亚金]]。<ref name="regulations">{{Cite web |url=https://www.fide.com/FIDE/handbook/regulations_match_2016.pdf |title=2016 Fide World Championship Match Regulations |accessdate=2016-11-17 |archive-date=2020-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407195842/https://www.fide.com/FIDE/handbook/regulations_match_2016.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

比赛于11月11日至30日间在美国[[纽约市|纽约市]][[南街海港|南街海港]]的{{le|富尔顿市场大楼|Fulton Market Building}}举行。<ref name="wsj_aug08">[http://www.wsj.com/articles/world-chess-championship-to-be-played-at-south-street-seaport-1470715206?ref=%2Fnew-york-main WCC to be played at South Street Seaport] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/world-chess-championship-to-be-played-at-south-street-seaport-1470715206?ref=%2Fnew-york-main |date=20160822234115 }} (Wall Street Journal)</ref>在12局慢棋较量中双方战成6-6平，双方各赢下一盘，剩下10盘则都以平局告终。最终在快棋加赛中，卡尔森以3-1战胜卡尔亚金，卫冕成功。<ref>[https://en.chessbase.com/post/newsblog-wcc-carlsen-karjakin-2016-11-30-en Carlsen wins tie-break and remains World Champion!] {{Wayback|url=https://en.chessbase.com/post/newsblog-wcc-carlsen-karjakin-2016-11-30-en |date=20181212001619 }}, chessbase.com, 30-11-2016</ref>

